# 12. dig

## Purpose

`dig` (Domain Information Groper) is an advanced DNS lookup utility.

## Syntax

```bash
dig google.com
```

## What It Provides

- DNS records
- Authoritative DNS servers
- Query time
- Response details
- Name server information

## Common DNS Records

- A Record
- AAAA Record
- MX Record
- TXT Record
- CNAME Record

## Use Cases

- DNS investigations.
- Security assessments.
- DNS troubleshooting.

