# 14. Netcat (nc)

## Purpose

Netcat is known as the "Swiss Army Knife of Networking."

## Syntax

```bash
nc google.com 80
```

## Capabilities

- Port scanning
- Banner grabbing
- File transfers
- TCP communication
- UDP communication
- Listener creation

## Common Example

```bash
nc -lvnp 4444
```

## Use Cases

- Penetration testing.
- Service testing.
- Network troubleshooting.

